    <entry>
      <title>love is nothing but you</title>
      <link href="/2024/06/08/love-is-nothing-but-you/"/>
      <url>/2024/06/08/love-is-nothing-but-you/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>Love is, </p><p>before you, it means nothing to me at all.</p><p>after you, it means nothing to me if not you.</p><p>Love is not making a right choice once for all.</p><p>Love is making the same choice over and over again.</p><p><img src="https://chris8831-1327037588.cos.ap-beijing.myqcloud.com/pic/pic11.webp"></p>]]></content>
      
      
      
