    <entry>
      <title>I love you</title>
      <link href="/2024/06/06/I-love-you/"/>
      <url>/2024/06/06/I-love-you/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>When you love,what matters most is you,not your beloved.</p><p>When you love,you subconsciously give unconditionally.</p><p>Do reconcile with yourself with worrying about the anxiety of loss or hurt.</p><p>Just remember,every step you walk on the path of love counts.</p><p>You have made a gift for yourself, no need stressing over the delivery of it. </p><p>God konws better than you, always!</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
        <tags>
            
            <tag> love </tag>
            
        </tags>
      
