    <entry>
      <title>love is intangible but colorful</title>
      <link href="/2024/06/04/love-is-intangible-but-colorful/"/>
      <url>/2024/06/04/love-is-intangible-but-colorful/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="/assets/css/APlayer.min.css"><script src="/assets/js/APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>Love is fated at first sight.</p><p>Love is seeded at first encountering.</p><p>Love is with afflictions.</p><p>Love is with miracles.</p><p>Love is, no one can make me the way like you do.</p>]]></content>
      
      
      
